description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Health Innovation Network are looking for a Lead Analyst for their Informatics team.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;W&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;e are looking for an experienced and dynamic data analyst to lead on a range of ad hoc analytics projects. Candidates must have experience in manipulating and interpreting health and social care data from a range of sources, an exceptional understanding of how to collate high quality data, experience of database design and reporting tools and evidence of gaining insight from data and presenting data in succinct and clear ways including through data &lt;span&gt;visualizations&lt;/span&gt;, dashboards and reports.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Candidates will be expected to have experience of managing analytics project from idea through to final outputs using existing project management tools. They must be organised with the ability to manage a varied workload. They must be able to work to tight deadlines often at short notice. They must be able to work autonomously as well as part of a small team and be the key point of contact for a range of external clients.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;As part of the assessment process candidates will be expected to complete a computer based assessment as well as a formal interview conducted remotely.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NamePolly SinclairJob titleLead AnalystEmail addresspolly.sinclair@nhs.netAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions pertaining to the role, please email :polly.sinclair@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews are to commence between 23rd - 30th November&lt;/p&gt;
